<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Error 404 - Página No Encontrada | EduConecta</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        .error-container {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 2rem;
        }
        
        .error-content {
            max-width: 600px;
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }
        
        .error-code {
            font-size: 8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .error-title {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        
        .error-description {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .error-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .search-box {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 50px;
            padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }
        
        .search-box::placeholder {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
        }
        
        .helpful-links {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 2rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            margin-top: 2rem;
        }
        
        .links-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        
        .link-item {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: white;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }
        
        .link-item:hover {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }
        
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }
        }
        
        .floating-icon {
            animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <div class="error-content">
            <div class="floating-icon"><i class="material-icons">menu_book</i></div>
            
            <div class="error-code">404</div>
            
            <h1 class="error-title">¡Oops! Página No Encontrada</h1>
            
            <p class="error-description">
                La página que estás buscando parece haber desaparecido. 
                Quizás fue movida, eliminada o nunca existió.
            </p>
            
            <div class="error-actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary" style="background: white; color: #667eea;">
                    🏠 Ir al Inicio
                </a>
                <a href="/catalogo" class="btn btn-outline" style="border-color: white; color: white;">
                    <i class="material-icons">menu_book</i> Ver Cursos
                </a>
                <a href="/contacto" class="btn btn-outline" style="border-color: white; color: white;">
                    <i class="material-icons">forum</i> Contactar Soporte
                </a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="search-box-container">
                <input type="text" class="search-box" placeholder="<i class="material-icons">search</i> Buscar lo que necesitas..." />
            </div>
            
            <div class="helpful-links">
                <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><i class="material-icons">link</i> Enlaces Útiles</h3>
                <div class="links-grid">
                    <a href="/catalogo" class="link-item">
                        <span><i class="material-icons">local_library</i></span>
                        <span>Catálogo de Cursos</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/precios" class="link-item">
                        <span><i class="material-icons">payments</i></span>
                        <span>Planes y Precios</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/blog" class="link-item">
                        <span><i class="material-icons">edit</i></span>
                        <span>Blog Educativo</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/quienes-somos" class="link-item">
                        <span><i class="material-icons">business</i></span>
                        <span>Sobre Nosotros</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/auth" class="link-item">
                        <span>👤</span>
                        <span>Iniciar Sesión</span>
                    </a>
                    <a href="/contacto" class="link-item">
                        <span><i class="material-icons">email</i></span>
                        <span>Contacto</span>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div style="margin-top: 3rem; opacity: 0.7; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                <p>¿Necesitas ayuda? <a href="/soporte" style="color: white; text-decoration: underline;">Visita nuestro centro de ayuda</a></p>
                <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem;">Código de error: 404-001</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <script>
        // Auto-search functionality
        document.querySelector('.search-box').addEventListener('keypress', function(e) {
            if (e.key === 'Enter') {
                const searchTerm = e.target.value;
                if (searchTerm.trim()) {
                    window.location.href = `/catalogo?search=${encodeURIComponent(searchTerm)}`;
                }
            }
        });
        
        // Log 404 error for analytics
        console.log('404 Error:', {
            url: window.location.href,
            referrer: document.referrer,
            timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
            userAgent: navigator.userAgent
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
